  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n74/mode/1up">71</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n76/mode/1up">73</ref>.</p>
      <p>i-ḷ. "peyar ai oṭu ku" eṉṉuñ cūttirattu aiyeṉap peyar peṟṟa vēṟṟumaiccol iraṇṭāvatām. aḵtiyāṇṭuvariṉum viṉaiyum viṉaikkuṟippumākiya avviraṇṭu mutaṟkaṇṇun tōṉṟum, avai poruḷāka varum. e - ṟu.</p>
<p>u-m. kuṭattai vaṉaintāṉ; kuḻaiyai yuṭaiyaṉ eṉa varum.</p>
<p>eṇṇumuṟaiyāṉ iraṇṭāvateṉpatu peṟappaṭumāyiṉum, ikkuṟi tollāciriyar vaḻakkeṉpa taṟivittaṟku aiyeṉappeyariya vēṟṟumaikkiḷavi yiraṇṭāvateṉṟār. itu mūṉṟāvatu mutalāyiṉavaṟṟiṟku mokkum.</p>
<p>peyariyaveṉpatu peyareṉpatu mutalāka muṭintatōr peyareccam.</p> 
<p>tammaiyuṇarttuvaṉavum peyareṉappaṭutaliṉ aiyeṉappeyariyaveṉṟār.</p>
<p>viṉaikkuṟippeṉṟārāyiṉum avaṟṟiṉ ceyappaṭuporuḷē koḷḷappaṭum; avviru mutaliṟ ṟōṉṟumeṉṟamaiyāṉ, mutalātaṟkum vēṟṟumaipporuḷātaṟkumēṟpaṉa avaiyēyākaliṉ. eṉṉai avaimutalātaṟ kēṟṟavāṟeṉiṉ:- ceyappaṭuporuṇmutalāyiṉa toḻiṟkuk kāraṇamākalāṉum, "āyeṭ ṭeṉpa toḻiṉ muta ṉilaiyē" eṉavavaṟṟai mutaṉilaiyeṉṟu kūṟupa vāka lāṉumeṉpatu. aḵtēl, ceyappaṭuporuḷāvatu toḻiṟ payaṉuṟuvatātalāl, kuḻai mutalāyiṉavaṟṟiṟku avvilakkaṇamēlāmaiyiṟ ceyappaṭuporuḷaṉmaiyāṉ viṉaikkuṟippeṉalvēṇṭāveṉiṉ:- aṟṟaṉṟu: "ammuk kālamuṅ kuṟippoṭu koḷḷu meynnilai yuṭaiya" eṉṟārākaliṉ, kuṟippuccoṟ kālamoṭu tōṉṟit toḻiṟcollātalum kuḻai mutalāyiṉa toḻiṟpayaṉuṟutalum āciriyar tuṇipākaliṉ, avaiyuñ ceyappaṭuporuḷā meṉpatu. āyiṉ, ceyappaṭuporuṭkaṭṭōṉṟumeṉavamaiyum, viṉaiyē viṉaikkuṟippeṉalvēṇṭāveṉiṉ:- aṅṅaṉaṅkūṟiṉ, ceyappāṭiṉitu viḷaṅkuñ ciṟappuṭait terinilaiviṉaic ceyappaṭuporuḷaiyē kūṟiṉārō kuṟippup poruḷumaṭaṅkap potuvakaiyāṟ kūṟiṉārōveṉṟaiyamām; aiyanīṅka viṉaiyē viṉaikkuṟippeṉṟāreṉpatu. viṉai viṉaikkuṟippeṉpaṉa īṇṭākupeyar.</p>
<p>pukaḻai niṟuttāṉ, pukaḻai niṟuttal; pukaḻai yuṭaiyāṉ, pukaḻai yuṭaimai eṉa viraṇṭāvatu peyaroṭu toṭarntavaḻiyum viṉaicceyappaṭuporuḷuṅ kuṟippuc ceyappaṭu poruḷumpaṟṟiyē niṟkumeṉpār, evvaḻi variṉumeṉṟiyāppuṟuttār.</p>
<p>iyaṟṟappaṭuvatum, vēṟupaṭukkappaṭuvatum, eytappaṭuvatumeṉac ceyappaṭuporuṇ mūṉṟām. iyaṟṟutalāvatu muṉṉillataṉaiyuṇṭākkutal. vēṟupaṭuttalāvatu muṉṉuḷḷataṉait tirittal. eytappaṭutalāvatu iyaṟṟutalum vēṟupaṭuttalumiṉṟit toḻiṟpayaṉuṟun tuṇaiyāy niṟṟal.	(10)</p>
    </body>
